      "side": 1,
      "message": "It may be devicePath().getBounds().round() or roundOut() depending on the draw\u0027s AA. non-AA uses round unless it lands close enough to 0.5 boundaries that we switch to out to play it conservative since we don\u0027t know how the GPU would snap. AA always rounds out.",
